### Create a tweet [POST]

+ text (string) - Text.

+ Request (application/json)

        { 
            "text": "Burp"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /posts/1

    + Body
    
            { 
                "id": 5, 
                "user": "New Guy",
                "text": "Greetings !" 
            }

## Posts [/posts/{id}]


+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... id of a post in form of an integer
        


### Delete a tweet [DELETE]

+ Response 204
